      "Case Number": "CGC00310082",
      "Case Title": "CHILDERS VS S.J. AMOROSO CONTRUCTION",
      "Court Date": "2002-01-11 09:30 AM",
      "Calendar Matter": "MOTION FOR SUMMARY JUDGMENT",
      "Rulings": "DEFENDANT'S (COFAB) MOTION FOR SUMMARY JUDGMENT - DENY, TRIABLE ISSUE OF FACT RE WHETHER THE CONTRACT REQUIRED FIELD OR SHOP WELDING. WHILE COFAB ARGUES THAT TUTOR'S PURCHASE ORDER REQUIRED SHOP WELDING, COFAB'S SEPARATE STATEMENT FAILS TO HIGHLIGHT WHAT CONTRACT PROVISION REQUIRED SHOP WELDING. THE SEPARATE STATEMENT MERELY REFERS TO DEPOSITION TESTIMONY AND THE RECORD IS COMPOSED OF CONTRADICTORY DEPOSITION TESTIMONY. (PB)"
    },
    {
      "Case Number": "CGC00310082",
      "Case Title": "CHILDERS VS S.J. AMOROSO CONTRUCTION",
      "Court Date": "2002-01-11 09:30 AM",
      "Calendar Matter": "MOTION FOR SUMMARY JUDGMENT",
      "Rulings": "DEFENDANT'S (TUTOR) MOTION FOR SUMMARY JUDGMENT - DENY, TRIABLE ISSUE OF FACT RE WHETHER TUTOR HAD THE DISCRETION TO ORDER FIELD WELDING AND IF SO, WHETHER THE FAILURE TO ORDER SUCH FIELD WELDING WAS A BREACH OF THE STANDARD OF CARE. (PB)"
    },
